name: Timbuk2 Tail Light Seat Pack
description: Ready for rides of any length, the Tail Light Seat Pack expands to carry an extra jacket or snacks, or cinches small for rides when you only need a patch kit.Rolltop closure expands to carry extra volume and seals tight to protect your gear from weather.Hook-and-loop straps attach easily to your bike.Timbuk2's signature Vista loop lets you clip on a blinky light.Reflective hits keep you visible in low light.
